Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 03:44:01 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] perf(frontend): route code-splitting (lazy-load all pages)

Convert all 58 page imports in the router to React.lazy and wrap routes
in Suspense. Result: the initial JS chunk drops from ~1.36MB to ~598KB
(-56%), and heavy code is split into per-route chunks loaded on demand:
EventForm (datepicker) 188KB, LocationMap (Leaflet) 153KB, TicketPage
(qrcode) 21KB, admin/organizer/wallet pages separate. Guests no longer
download admin/organizer/map/form code they never use.
---
 Frontend/src/app/router/AppRouter.jsx | 124 +++++++++++++-------------
 1 file changed, 63 insertions(+), 61 deletions(-)

